{"tid":2089360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO 要走要留都唔割","createTime":"2020-07-01T15:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T15:51:24.000Z","uid":169262,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e679fb30edb9ecb6260d50a14dfba4794425b1f2","tid":2089360,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"夠資格拎 咪拎左先，<br />\n本身英國欠我地，佢賣左香港人比老共，<br />\nBNO無論如何都要拎<br />\n<br />\n講到明佢個立法程序要幾個月<br />\n到時局勢係點無人知<br />\n<br />\n一個唔好彩 到時要開戰，<br />\n咪講咩sir this way，咩參戰<br />\n老共一定拎香港人做人貭<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n另一邊 拎BNO就當被捕手足condom<br />\n去到外國一樣可以打國際線<br />\n總之唔好忘記香港仲有人係水深火熱之中<br />\n建立香港民族 唔單只係香港建立<br />\n你咪當自己好似 d咩同鄉會咁 在當地建立團體<br />\n//<br />\nsor for 1999<br />\n請屌細力d"},{"pid":"e3a8bb4a88ab7dad85599664bc173cfc44a6bdb7","tid":2089360,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"中產黃絲要走都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定要搵方法救埋小朋友走<br />\n唔想見到大家辛苦ot搵錢 變成繳稅維穩打細路<br />\n賺錢養gestapo 不如齊上齊落逃出香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842d445993da409d7aad1294bca6c0c62c17e0f5","tid":2089360,"uid":260694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"去英國唔係為咗自己，係為咗下一代。"},{"pid":"5660d2bbc1e2ed4dfd518e2abcb8d0537b20e989","tid":2089360,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:49:15.000Z","msg":"小推5"},{"pid":"ae7bdeda890b56092dd6c6cee3378260567f3adb","tid":2089360,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"f4aba8eb2d384dd6da48b301fb082135a355f633","tid":2089360,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4e4e5fb4669b28438008ff3f69d5503ff2b32264","tid":2089360,"uid":16926